  "body": "<div id=\"post-view110187967563\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea110187967563\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:10pt; font-family:'957317_10';\" class=\"view\"><div style=\"font-size:10pt; font-family:'957317_10';\" class=\"view\"><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/b286dee20ecc8fd6.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"469\" style=\"cursor: pointer;border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); rheight: 500px; rwidth: 586px;\" id=\"20140328_57/isuhani_139597780623694SWY_JPEG/P3282716.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7B6F44B')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/b286dee20ecc8fd6.jpg\"></div><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style='font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>어제는 오렌지를, 오늘 오전에는 맛있는 모카스폰지케이크를 선물로 주셨습니다^^</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style='font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>최근에 치료받는 증상이 호전이 되어서 그런지 내원하는 횟수가 뜸해지셨는데</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style='font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>&nbsp;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style='font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>오늘 근처에 지나가는길에 케이크 주려고 잠깐 들렀다고 하시네요~</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style='font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>&nbsp;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style='font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>기분좋은 햇살만큼이나 가볍고 밝아진 표정을보니 저희도 덩달아 밝아지는 하루입니다.<img src=\"https://ssl.pstatic.net/static.se2/static/full/20130612/emoticon/1_05.gif\" onload=\"setTimeout('utility.resizeImageWithId(\\'static\\/full\\/20130612\\/emoticon\\/1_05.gif\\')',200)\" style=\"cursor: pointer;\" id=\"static/full/20130612/emoticon/1_05.gif\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7B6F44B')\" alt=\"\"></span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n </div></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
